nodes.text: Lord Wullo Humbonnen was a Human male aristocrat of Naboo who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

Dialogue pertaining to Wullo Humbonnen appeared in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. However, he never actually appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character.
